---
// Giscus 评论系统组件（基于 GitHub Discussions，无需后端）
// 访客用 GitHub 账号登录后即可直接在文章末尾留言
---

<section id="comments" class="giscus-comments mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--button-border-color)] scroll-mt-24" aria-label="评论">
  <h2 class="giscus-title text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-color)] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
    </svg>
    <span>评论</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="giscus"></div>
</section>

<script is:inline data-astro-rerun>
  // 动态加载 Giscus 评论系统
  // is:inline + data-astro-rerun：Astro View Transitions 切换页面后会重新执行，
  // 保证每次进入文章页都会按当前 pathname 重新初始化 Giscus。

  const GISCUS_CONFIG = {
    src: 'https://giscus.app/client.js',
    repo: 'shi-tou1234/-',
    repoId: 'R_kgDORRKvYA',
    // 必须使用普通讨论分类，公告类（Announcements）只允许维护者发帖，
    // 访客点击发表会没有响应。
    category: 'General',
    categoryId: 'DIC_kwDORRKvYM4DAamD',
    mapping: 'pathname',
    strict: '0',
    reactionsEnabled: '1',
    emitMetadata: '0',
    inputPosition: 'top',
    theme: 'preferred_color_scheme',
    lang: 'zh-CN',
  };

  function loadGiscus() {
    const container = document.querySelector('#comments .giscus');
    if (!container) return;

    // 已存在 iframe 说明已经初始化过，直接跳过
    if (container.querySelector('iframe.giscus-frame')) return;

    // View Transitions 切换后容器内可能残留过期脚本，先清空
    container.innerHTML = '';

    const script = document.createElement('script');
    script.src = GISCUS_CONFIG.src;
    script.crossOrigin = 'anonymous';
    script.async = true;
    script.setAttribute('data-repo', GISCUS_CONFIG.repo);
    script.setAttribute('data-repo-id', GISCUS_CONFIG.repoId);
    script.setAttribute('data-category', GISCUS_CONFIG.category);
    script.setAttribute('data-category-id', GISCUS_CONFIG.categoryId);
    script.setAttribute('data-mapping', GISCUS_CONFIG.mapping);
    script.setAttribute('data-strict', GISCUS_CONFIG.strict);
    script.setAttribute('data-reactions-enabled', GISCUS_CONFIG.reactionsEnabled);
    script.setAttribute('data-emit-metadata', GISCUS_CONFIG.emitMetadata);
    script.setAttribute('data-input-position', GISCUS_CONFIG.inputPosition);
    script.setAttribute('data-theme', GISCUS_CONFIG.theme);
    script.setAttribute('data-lang', GISCUS_CONFIG.lang);

    container.appendChild(script);
  }

  function syncGiscusTheme() {
    const iframe = document.querySelector('#comments .giscus iframe.giscus-frame');
    if (!iframe) return;
    const currentTheme = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme') || 'light';
    const giscusTheme = currentTheme === 'dark' ? 'dark' : 'light';
    iframe.contentWindow.postMessage(
      { giscus: { setConfig: { theme: giscusTheme } } },
      'https://giscus.app'
    );
  }

  function init() {
    loadGiscus();

    // 主题变化监听（只注册一次）
    if (!window.__giscusThemeObserver) {
      window.__giscusThemeObserver = new MutationObserver(syncGiscusTheme);
      window.__giscusThemeObserver.observe(document.documentElement, {
        attributes: true,
        attributeFilter: ['data-theme'],
      });
    }
  }

  // 初始加载
  init();

  // View Transitions 页面切换后重新加载
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', init);

  // 监听 Giscus 报错，方便在浏览器控制台查看具体原因
  window.addEventListener('message', function onGiscusMessage(event) {
    if (event.origin !== 'https://giscus.app') return;
    const data = event.data && event.data.giscus;
    if (data && data.error) {
      console.error('[Giscus error]', data.error);
    }
  });
</script>

<style is:global>
  .giscus-comments {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .giscus {
    min-height: 12rem;
  }

  .giscus iframe.giscus-frame {
    width: 100%;
    border: none;
    color-scheme: light dark;
  }
</style>
